reviews.text: Aways visit once a year for Leaders Conference. It's like coming home. Love these guys. #unity

This is my regular church. People are friendly and the subject of God is always discussed in a down to earth fashion, and events from the Bible are explained in a clear and usually uncomplicated way. I recommend everyone go and see for themselves!! Children are also made very welcome.
Home of Alpha courses.  Made very welcome. Good acoustics. Set down long drive & not visible from street. Awkward to find as first time visitors even with GPS
The best Anglican Church for understanding the work if the Holy Spirit. Open. Honest. Down to earth. Welcoming. Super super church. Recommend it. 10 stars!
For those who want to know Jesus Christ, the place I highly recommend to visit on Sunday mornings at 9am or 11am.
